<CATEGORY> international </CATEGORY>
<HEADLINE>  Iranian President Visits Italy </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	ROME (AP) -- Iran is ready for a new era of East-West friendship,  
President Mohammad Khatami said in a groundbreaking visit to Italy. 
</P>
<P>
	Khatami arrived in Italy on Tuesday to a warm welcome and the  
tightest security the capital has seen in years. He was to meet 
today with Italy's premier and has an audience with the pope on 
Thursday. 
</P>
