<CATEGORY> sports </CATEGORY>
<HEADLINE>  Now Stanford's Vulnerable in NCAAs </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	SEATTLE (AP) -- Stanford's regular season ended ingloriously with  
a 14-point loss at Oregon State. In February, the Cardinal were 
embarrassed by an 11-point home loss to a Connecticut team missing 
its best player. 
